premise_source_doc_sentence: Detroit  (  -LSB- dᵻˈtrɔɪt -RSB-  )  is the most populous city in the U.S. state of Michigan , the largest city on the United States -- Canada border , and the seat of Wayne County .

After a devastating fire in 1805 , Augustus B. Woodward devised a street plan similar to Pierre Charles L'Enfant 's design for Washington , D.C. Detroit 's monumental avenues and traffic circles fan out in radial fashion from Campus Martius Park in the heart of the city , which facilitates traffic patterns along the city 's tree-lined boulevards and parks .
